This paper is about evaluating translation models using a neural text classifier and neural explainability methods. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which deals with natural language processing and computational linguistics. The paper also uses machine learning techniques, so cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) are also likely sub-categories. Additionally, the paper uses neural explainability methods, which are often used in computer vision, so cs.CV (Computer Vision) is a possible sub-category. Finally, the paper uses adversarial settings, which are often used in neural networks, so cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is also a possible sub-category.
